# Swift compiler artifacts from SourceKit-LSP's index build. When the
# IDE indexer compiles a build-plugin-generated source file (like
# Wire's `_<Name>WireGraph.swift`), the per-source artifacts (`.d`,
# `.dia`, `.o`, `.swiftdeps`) sometimes land at the project root
# instead of inside `.build/`. Harmless; just keep them out of
# version control.
/_*WireGraph.*
